# NoteStream — project context

macOS-only lecture notes app with **local transcription** and **system audio capture**.

## Non-negotiables (v1)

- Prefer **Swift / SwiftUI** over web frontends.
- Capture uses **ScreenCaptureKit** (system audio) + **AVFoundation** (conversion).
- Transcription uses **WhisperKit** locally.
- Market v1 as **rolling transcription** (updates every few seconds) + **final cleanup after stop**.
- Do **not** implement SwiftData/CoreData in v1. Persist sessions as **folders + JSON + Markdown**.

## Product principle

**The live transcript can lag, but it must not jump.**

